  "description": "Carrot/parsley/umbellifer family — ~434 genera, ~3,780 species. Diagnostic compound umbel inflorescence, hollow stems, aromatic compounds (furanocoumarins, essential oils), schizocarp fruit splitting into two mericarps. Includes both essential foods and deadly poisons.",
